
*** Settings ***
Library    SeleniumLibrary
#Resource    ../Rescourse/Rescourse.py
Documentation    This file is for testing ABC feature

*** Variables ***
${Browser}  Chrome
${URL}    http://www.YYYYY.com/
${URL_1}    https://www.XXXXX.com
${UserNamet}    ABC
${Password}      xxxx
${waitingTime}  5 seconds
${Page Contains}    Login
${screenShot}  ./Screenshot/TC_001.png



*** Test Cases ***
TC_001 Login Page
    [Documentation]    This test case for validate Login

    [Setup]           Open Browsers    ${URL}   ${Browser}     ${Page Contains}
    [Teardown]        Close Browser    ${screenShot}
                      Login Page       ${UserNamet}     ${Password}     ${waitingTime}



*** Keywords ***
Open Browsers
    #[Documentation]     This t
    [Arguments]    ${URL}   ${Browser}     ${Page Contains}
    Open Browser     ${URL}  ${Browser}
    page should contain   ${Page Contains}
    Maximize Browser Window
    set selenium implicit wait    ${waitingTime}

Close Browser
    [Arguments]     ${screenShot}
    seleniumlibrary.capture page screenshot    ${screenShot}
    close all browsers

Login Page
    [Arguments]    ${UserNamet}     ${Password}     ${waitingTime}
    seleniumlibrary.input text   login   ${UserNamet}
    seleniumlibrary.input password    password     ${Password}
    seleniumlibrary.click button    //input[@value="sign-in"]
    set selenium implicit wait      ${waitingTime}
    get window handles





